# Conan 2 generated files
# NOTE: gitignore only treats '#' as a comment at the START of a line — a
# trailing '#...' is part of the pattern, not a comment. This entry previously
# carried an inline comment, which made it match a filename that literally
# contained that text, i.e. it ignored nothing and the generated file below was
# left untracked-but-committable.
# Generated by conanfile.py init() — DO NOT COMMIT.
ConanLibImports.cmake
CMakeUserPresets.json
conan_toolchain.cmake
conandeps_legacy.cmake
*Config.cmake
*ConfigVersion.cmake
*Targets*.cmake
find*.cmake
build/generators/

